quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Obutswenufu ni bwa ulia owayila Omusumba wuwe eshilo okhurula khumusikiti kwoluyali okhula khumusikiti kwa ehale okwa khwahelesia tsikhabi ebili mumbeka tsiakwo, kho khumwechesie bilala khubimanyisio biefu. Toto ye niwokhuwulila po, Owokhulola muno."
  17,2,"Ne khwahelesia Musa Eshitabu, ne nikhushikhola obulunjifu khubana ba Israili mbu; “Mulakhola omulindi wundi ulali esie tawe.”"
  17,3,"Olwibulo lwa balia bakhwachinga halala nende Nuh. Toto ye yali Omusumba wokhupa orio muno."
  17,4,"Ne khwabusilia Abana ba Israili mushitabu mbu; ‘‘Toto enywe mwitsa okhukhola obwononi khushialo khabiri, ne toto mana mulikhola obufuru obukhongo.”"
  17,5,"Mana olwa yiliula indache ya obwononi bwa imbeli, khulibarerera Abasumba befu abalwani abatinyu, nabo balinjila mutsingo tsienyu buli elubeka, ne ino ni indache iliikholekha."
  17,6,"Mana khulibakalusilia enywe obushiri khubo, ne khulibametela omwandu nende Abana, ne khulibakhola mube omukanda omunji."
  17,7,"Nimukhola amalayi, mwikholelanga abeene. Ne nimukhola amabii, mwikholelanga abeene. Ne olwa indache ya obwononi bwokhumalilikha yiliula, kho banyoole okhunyasia obweni bwenyu, ne benjile mumusikiti shingala benjilangamwo lwamberi, ne kho banyasie okhunyasia okhukhongo bioosi biababukula."